  message: Workflow triggered by pr with secret/identity access — 2 step(s) hold authority that attacker-controlled code could reach
  recommendation:
    type: manual
    action: "Use a separate workflow triggered by workflow_run (not pull_request_target) for privileged operations, or ensure no checkout of the PR head ref occurs before secret use"
